# UniTEA

Minimal game engine to play games[^1] on your text editor.
[^1]: we call these games "text-edit adventures", or TEAs.

## Install

```sh
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
```
Note that you may have to install per-game dependencies, but related information will be shown when needed.

## Run

```sh
source venv/bin/activate
python3 unitea/unitea.py game.txt
```

Then open `game.txt` with your text editor, or open it with our sample minimal editor:
```sh
python3 unitea/unitea-editor.py game.txt
```

## Play

Enter one of the following in the editor and save file:
```
tictactoe
hangman abomination
ink unitea/games/ink/example/intercept.ink.json
```

## Adding Game

To add a new game 'MyGame':
```bash
python3 unitea/unitea.py --create mygame
```

